
QuantLib: a free/open-source library for quantitative finance
URL: https://www.quantlib.org/

=========================================================================
installation: (Tested on Ubuntu 20)

sudo apt update
sudo apt install build-essential git cmake libboost-all-dev

# Clone the official QuantLib repository
git clone https://github.com/lballabio/quantlib.git
cd quantlib

# Create a build directory
mkdir build && cd build

# Configure with CMake
cmake ..

# Build the library
make -j$(nproc)

# (Optional) Install system-wide
sudo make install
==========================================================================

$g++ -std=c++17 main.cpp -o test -lQuantLib
$export LD_LIBRARY_PATH=/usr/local/lib:$LD_LIBRARY_PATH
$./test

========================================================================
scp shiv@192.168.xx.xx:/home/shiv/quantlib-test/* .